---+ Stick of BEE +---

The stick of BEE is a legendary artifact said to have been created from the INFINI BEE itself 

its also said to have BEEn from the first tree created in the honeyland

some say with a swipe of the stick of BEE you can create a honey forest within seconds

combined with the honey of truth it can be a powerful weapon



---+ The honey of truth +---

it is said the honey of truth came from the first hive of the first tree of the honeyland

when consumed the honey of truth will force whatever consumed it to tell the truth the amount of time depends on how much they consume

when combined with the stick of BEE it will summon a swarm of Truth Bees that will swarm a target.



---+ Stick of Truth +---

This is less an artifact more of a combination of two artifacts

the stick of BEE
and
the Honey of Truth

when the Honey of Truth is smeared onto the Stick of Truth it creates the Stick of Truth

with a wave of this Stick it will summon a swarm of Truth Bees which will obay the summoners will unless the INFINI BEE gets involved

the INFINI BEE is all mighty and his will is un deniable


